observations.recommendation:
We recommend that the Local Chief Executive require the GAD Focal Person
to plan, focus and undertake definite activities such as:
 Enhancement of women’s access to all types of health care;
 Lowering of maternal mortality rates and provide adequate family
planning services;
 Improvement of the situation of women in the informal economy;
 Creating awareness for women who are victims of violence to report their
ordeal, to proper authorities.
This is without prejudice to the issuance of Notice of Suspension and/or Notice of
Disallowance.
